Package: rOceanData
Title: rOceanData: a package to simplify downloading, extracting, and visualising ocean satellite data
Version: 0.1.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Roff", , "george.roff@csiro.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2823-0575"))
License: GPL (>= 3)
Description: The rOceanData package is a collection of "user friendly" functions that simplify downloading, extracting, 
    and visualising global ocean satellite datasets (NOAA CRW, HadISST) for non-oceanographers. The functions facilitate downloading .netCDF files 
    from THREDDS Data Servers, extracting, subsetting, and processing data to .csv and spatraster formats, and mapping global 
    datasets using the terra package. 
